Commentary Text: Avesh Khan to Hardik Pandya, out Caught by de Kock!! Edged and caught Hardik stands there in disbelief, he doesn't want to go, but there was a clear edge and it would have been foolhardy to review this, stands there for a long time and then trudges back to the dug-out. This was short and this was wide of off, was there to be put away, but Hardik in eagerness went too hard on the cut, gets a thick top-edge and it's a dolly for the keeper. Big big moment in the game, Hardik was one batter who could have ensured a fighting score on this pitch. Hardik Pandya c de Kock b Avesh Khan 11(13)
